<odoo>
    <template id="bigboxes_snippet" name="BigBoxes Snippet">
        <section class="bigboxes_snippet">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 o_cc o_cc3 text-center o_colored_level">
                        <img class="img_box" src="https://api.iconify.design/noto:recycling-symbol.svg"/>
                        <h2>A color block</h2>
                        <p>Color blocks are a simple and effective way to <b>present and highlight your content</b>. Choose an image or a color for the background. You can even resize and duplicate the blocks to create your own layout. Add images or icons to customize the blocks.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mb-2">More Details</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 o_cc o_cc5 text-center o_colored_level">
                        <img class="img_box" src="https://api.iconify.design/fxemoji:americasglobe.svg"/>
                        <h2>Another color block</h2>
                        <p>Color blocks are a simple and effective way to <b  >present and highlight your content</b>. Choose an image or a color for the background. You can even resize and duplicate the blocks to create your own layout. Add images or icons to customize the blocks.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mb-2">More Details</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </template>
    <template id="place_boxes_into_bar" inherit_id="website.snippets" name="Place boxes into bar">
        <xpath expr="//div[@id='snippet_structure']/div[hasclass('o_panel_body')]" position="inside">
            <t t-snippet="theme_test.bigboxes_snippet"
                    t-thumbnail="/website/static/src/img/snippets_thumbs/s_color_blocks_2.svg"/>
        </xpath>
    </template>
</odoo>